Granite looks around him, he was surrounded. Technosis fiddled with a
blaster, she was never a good fighter, which is why Deemos grew so impatient
with her. Atma on the other hand, WAS a VERY good fighter! Atma fires away
at Serge. Serge growled and spun around to face Atma. Atma started building
MP for Ultima. Serge kncoked him down and pinned him, firing away at his
head as Atma tried to cover himself.

"Which one do you want, Sharpedge? How about that one?" Deemos says. He
points at Granite.

"He's a new one, back on Cybertron he killed many, but here, he has lost his
edge, no hiding spots!" Deemos says...
